title: E130 TIM DILLON IS FUNNY - IMPAULSIVE EP. 130
itunes:title: TIM DILLON IS FUNNY - IMPAULSIVE EP. 130
description:
Stand-up comedian Tim Dillon has three fears: Lilly Singh, Greta Thunberg, and Cincinnati. In this episode, Tim addresses a full-proof way to avoid being “cancelled,” how he convinces people that he’s NOT Chris Farley, and the effectiveness of a well balanced Keto diet. Get ready to laugh.
